# Frontend Standards

## Data Layer

- API calls in `src/api/` only. Components use TanStack Query hooks, not direct fetch.
- Mirror backend types in `src/api/types.ts`.
- Parse API error envelope into typed `ApiError`; show user-friendly messages.

## Components

- Use shadcn/ui + Tailwind; `cn()` for class merging.
- Functional components; extract hooks for reusable logic.
- Protected routes via `ProtectedRoute`; auth state in `AuthContext`.

## UX

- Loading and error states on every async view.
- Form validation aligned with backend rules (title length, password rules, etc.).
- Dark mode via `ThemeContext`; responsive layout with sidebar navigation.

## Tests

- Vitest + React Testing Library; MSW for API mocking.
- Test behavior, not implementation details.
